data.description: Grand entrance to this rambler style home with lots of natural light with vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, large open kitchen with center island and stainless steel appliances, beautiful gas fireplace with brick surround and built ins.  Newer composite deck off of your dining area.  Large 3 car garage leads you into your mudroom/laundry area and into your kitchen.  Main floor primary bedroom with ensuite bath with separate tub and shower, dual sinks and tiled floor plus a large walk in closet.  2nd bedroom on main level could make a great office/den if needed.  Lower level walkout has a huge family room that leads out to your stamped concrete patio.  2 large bedrooms on separate ends of the space.  There is also a large unfinished room that would make a great movie theater room, or?  Also a 3/4 bath and large utility room with storage.  The back yard is partially fenced in thanks to a few of the neighbor's fences, so less fence needed to fully fence in the back yard!  Hurry Home!
